name: Complete Project Proposal
description: Write a detailed proposal outlining project scope, objectives, and deliverables.

name: Design User Interface Mockups
description: Create wireframes and design mockups for the project's user interface.

name: Implement Backend APIs
description: Develop RESTful APIs to handle backend functionality and data management.

name: Write Unit Tests
description: Create unit tests to ensure code quality and functionality.

name: Refactor Codebase
description: Review and refactor existing code for improved readability and performance.

name: Prepare Presentation Slides
description: Create slides for project presentation summarizing key points and progress.

name: Test Application on Multiple Devices
description: Conduct comprehensive testing of the application on various devices and platforms.

name: Document API Endpoints
description: Create documentation detailing available API endpoints and request/response formats.

name: Review User Feedback
description: Collect and analyze user feedback to identify areas for improvement.

name: Deploy Application to Production
description: Deploy the finalized application to production servers for public access.
